What is this project?
--> This is a server for a chat application I made, it is somewhat a game more than it is an actual app
    users have levels and points with each level they gain points to buy stickers, experience points
    are gained when sending messages to other users

How to run?
--> Create a mongo db database named chatGame
--> Create a .env file
--> Fill it with these variables:
        DATABASE_URL = the mongo db connection url
        JWT_SECRET   = a secret string to encode authentication tokens with
        EMAIL        = the email to be used to send automatic emails to users
        EMAILPASS    = the password provided by your email service to enable automatic emails sending
--> npm install
--> run mongo server
--> npm run